ield--name-localgov-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"},["H2",{"id":"collection-of-bins"},"Collection of bins"],"\n",["P",{},["STRONG",{},"Have your bin out by 6:30am on the day of collection."]," Remember that the council operates a \"no side waste\" policy - any waste (bagged or loose) placed at the side of your bins will not be taken. "],"\n",["P",{},"If you know which day of the week your bins are collected, you can download a calendar for your bin days below."],"\n",["P",{},"For garden waste (brown bins), the district is split into two collections: week 1 and week 2. You will know which week you are when you receive your garden waste sticker if you ",["A",{"href":"/bins-waste-recycling/report-or-request-waste-service/garden-waste-service","data-entity-type":"node","data-entity-uuid":"911b28d5-cd98-4e97-a2c0-d130ab64d787","data-entity-substitution":"canonical"},"sign up to the garden waste service"],". "],"\n",["P",{},["SPAN",{"style":"color:#444444;font-family:\"PT Sans\",sans-serif;font-size:12.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;"},"You can also "],["A",{"href":"https://www.n-kesteven.org.uk/bins"},"search for your bin days by postcode"],"."]],"\n      \n      "],"\n"],"\n      "],"\n              ",["DIV",{"class":"field__item"},"\n            ",["DIV",{"class":"field field--name-label field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item"},"accordion | find your bin collection day 25/26"],"\n      \n            ",["DIV",{"class":"field field--name-paragraphs field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__item"},"\n\n\n\n  ",["DIV",{"data-id":"paragraphs-localgov_accordion-4215","class":"paragraph paragraph--type--localgov-accordion paragraph--view-mode--default accordion accordion--initialised"},"\n          ",["H2",{},"Bin day calendars 2025/26"],"\n            \n      ",["DIV",{"class":"field field--n